
brief:      "Halden — a single-origin coffee roastery in Bergen that roasts one lot at a time and names the farm on every bag. A cinematic scroll story about the journey from a hillside in Huila to the cup: the altitude, the hands that pick it, the roast curve, the pour. Mood: premium, calm, cinematic."
reasoning:  claude-sonnet-5   (questions · concept · plan · art-direction)
bulk:       claude-sonnet-5   (section codegen · self-critique; escalates to reasoning on repair)
design:     claude-haiku-4-5-20251001   (legacy/fallback tier)

