  register floor (editorial-story): added missing beat(s) — close
brand:  Halden
mood:   premium, calm
layout: origin-to-proof, editorial-brand-story
sections:
  0. the-hillside     [36mcinematic[0m/xl  Open on the origin itself: a specific hillside in Huila, establishing altitude and place before any brand claim is made
  1. the-hands        [36mnarrative[0m/lg  Name the farm and the picker — credit the specific people and lot rather than an abstract 'sourced ethically' claim
  2. elevation-notes  [36meditorial[0m/md  Give the altitude and lot data its own quiet, factual moment — the numbers that explain the flavor
  3. the-crossing     [36masymmetric[0m/md  Bridge from farm to roastery — the lot's journey from Huila to Bergen, one shipment, one bag at a time
  4. the-roast-curve  [36mcinematic[0m/xl  Make the roast itself the anchor moment — the single most dramatic beat of the whole story, the transformation of the bean
  5. the-pour         [36mnarrative[0m/lg  Land in the cup — the moment of drinking, closing the loop from hillside to hand
  6. the-bag          [36mmodular[0m/md  Present proof: the actual bag with the farm name printed on it, plus how to get the current single lot
  7. close            [36meditorial[0m/md  land the ending; a story that stops is not a story that closes

